        <MadCap:dropDown>
            <MadCap:dropDownHead class="OnlineOnly">
                <MadCap:dropDownHotspot>Note</MadCap:dropDownHotspot>
            </MadCap:dropDownHead>
            <MadCap:dropDownBody>
                <div class="note">
                    <p class="Note-Text" MadCap:autonum="&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #242729;&quot; class=&quot;mcFormatColor&quot;&gt;Note &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;">In the Theme Designer, you can also create a new theme by clicking the <span class="Emphasis">Add New Theme</span> button <img src="../../../../Images/D2H/Interface/Buttons/Add-Theme-btn.png" height="16" class="ReduceButtonSize" />.</p>
